summary: the fact that Michael keeps on retwitting fanarts and complimenting the artists who made them makes me cry because even if I’m...
body:
the fact that Michael keeps on retwitting fanarts and complimenting the artists who made them makes me cry because even if I’m not an artist I can imagine the happiness you get whenever someone acknowledges your skills.

So, in conclusion, this man is a blessing.
